        {
            "title": "聯準會洛根表示央行應避免釋出降息傾向訊號",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 達拉斯聯邦儲備銀行總裁洛麗·洛根(Lorie Logan)週五表示,鑑於經濟前景的不確定性和持續的通膨擔憂,央行不應釋出下一步政策行動將是降息的訊號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根解釋了她本週在聯邦公開市場委員會(FOMC)會議聲明中投下反對票的原因,稱鑑於當前貨幣政策面臨的雙向風險,聯準會不應提供暗示偏好降息的前瞻性指引。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她與另外兩位地區聯儲銀行總裁一同投票反對暗示聯準會下一步行動將是降息的措辭。洛根支持聯準會將利率目標維持在3.5%至3.75%之間的決定。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bbb07824-19fe-392e-974e-442335cbfcdc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,在通膨回歸2%目標的持續擔憂下,經濟前景高度不確定。鑑於當前展望,FOMC的下一次利率變動可能是升息或降息,她說。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,她對將通膨率降回2%越來越感到擔憂,同時指出就業市場一直保持穩定。她補充說,通膨路徑的前景仍不確定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,當FOMC提供前瞻性指引時,該指引必須反映政策展望,這一點非常重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%9B%E6%A0%B9%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%87%89%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%87%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F-150608585.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 23:30:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "為何布蘭特原油價格未大幅飆升?Yardeni發表看法",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wwIi1eNosr5D3CRzCCFOrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_2_M_1440048332.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 自2月28日起荷莫茲海峽關閉,這是石油市場歷史上最大規模的供應中斷,導致全球供應減少逾15%,然而布蘭特原油僅小幅上漲至90美元至100美元區間。Yardeni Research對此作出解釋。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構指出六大因素緩和了許多分析師原本預期的更嚴重價格飆升,部分預測曾預計油價將達到每桶150美元至200美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首先,替代基礎設施發揮了作用。沙烏地阿拉伯和阿聯酋提升了管道運輸能力,合計每日輸送約700萬桶石油,而此前通過海峽運輸的石油量為每日1700萬至2000萬桶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dffe5d96-0720-3742-a9a6-c46c2affffb3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其次,來自伊朗和俄羅斯石油豁免的緊急供應、國際能源署戰略儲備釋放以及中國庫存轉售進一步緩衝了市場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第三,Yardeni表示全球價格只是故事的一半。\"雖然基準布蘭特原油價格維持在每桶100美元附近,但這並不代表全球油價的真實情況,\"該機構寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"運抵亞洲的杜拜原油價格曾飆升至每桶260美元。整個亞洲的當地買家正支付溢價。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">接下來,Yardeni指出需求破壞正在加速,國際能源署目前預測2026年全球石油需求將收縮8萬桶/日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第五,全球經濟的能源密集度據稱遠低於1970年代石油危機時期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後,石油期貨呈現陡峭的現貨溢價結構,顯示市場預期這是暫時性而非永久性的供應中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們預計今年剩餘時間布蘭特原油將在每桶85美元至100美元區間交易,高於衝突前水平,\"Yardeni寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構補充表示,只要長期通膨預期保持穩定,且工資-價格螺旋上升的風險維持在低水平,升息就不在考慮範圍內。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E7%89%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%AA%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-yardeni%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-155634321.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-02 00:37:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本政府二次干預匯市的可能性有多大?",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ekIenVtvHWNmH01B5WBbJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC3L0Q0_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國銀行的一份報告指出,日本最近為支撐日圓而進行的貨幣干預,可能在未來幾天內就會迎來第二輪行動,該報告強調了過去干預行動中反覆出現的模式。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外界普遍認為,日本政府在4月30日介入外匯市場,買入日圓並賣出美元。此舉引發日圓大幅升值,美元兌日圓匯率下跌約5日圓——從約160.6跌至155.6——跌幅與過去的干預幅度相當。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間10:14,日圓兌美元匯率小幅下跌至156.42美元,扭轉了前一交易日下跌逾2%的走勢。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f6fb4aeb-c72c-356f-a3dd-c3e2f51f6359-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一跌幅主要歸因於政府干預,東京方面被認為在美元兌日圓本週稍早突破160日圓後介入市場。該水平過去曾引發干預行動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從歷史上看,此類干預往往會在一至兩個交易日內進行第二輪行動。這些通常發生在貨幣對回撤其初始跌幅約50-70%之後。根據這一模式,分析師認為158-159區間是當局可能再次採取行動的關鍵區域。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,該報告警告稱,干預的整體影響可能只是暫時的。如果沒有持續的政策支持——特別是日本央行的加息——日圓可能會恢復走弱,隨著時間推移,美元兌日圓可能會重新推向160水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管市場仍將6月加息的可能性定價為約60%,但央行在4月決定維持利率不變,可能降低了干預的有效性。分析師認為,更強力的貨幣緊縮政策將加強政府穩定貨幣的努力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,干預為投資者和企業創造了戰術性機會。進口商可以利用走強的日圓來獲得美元資金,而其他人則可以對沖日圓進一步貶值的風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管可能出現額外的干預輪次,但美國銀行指出,日本可以採取的激進行動存在限制,包括外匯儲備保護和國際貨幣外交考量等制約因素。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E5%8C%AF%E5%B8%82%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7%E6%9C%89%E5%A4%9A%E5%A4%A7-153048284.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-02 00:37:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特斯拉歐洲銷量持續回升,燃料成本上漲推動電動車需求",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/weOb9x2EBbh8ZF9DpmLg7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC340AO_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特斯拉\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特斯拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特斯拉\">特斯拉</a>在歐洲部分市場的註冊量於4月份持續復甦,隨著伊朗戰爭後燃料價格飆升,丹麥、法國和荷蘭的銷量均有所增長,推動消費者對電動車的興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>特斯拉</span></span></span></span>在丹麥的4月份註冊量按年增長102%,根據bilstatistik.dk的數據顯示;而法國的註冊量則增長112%,根據PFA的數據。在荷蘭,汽車行業協會BOVAG報告稱,註冊量從去年的381輛增加23%至469輛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷蘭的數據公布不久前,該國車輛管理局RDW於4月10日對特斯拉的全自動駕駛輔助軟件發出臨時批准。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d8c6bb43-86e2-383f-9c8a-fbe52be4768c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">RDW此後已通知歐盟委員會,表示有意為該軟件尋求歐盟範圍內的批准,特斯拉通過月度訂閱方式提供該軟件。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4月份的數據為特斯拉在歐洲的強勁開局增添了動力,第一季度該公司在整個歐洲大陸的註冊量增長近45%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次回升是在連續兩年銷量下滑之後出現的,包括2025年下降近27%。自2月28日伊朗戰爭開始以來,電動車的興趣加速增長,推動該地區燃料價格走高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管出現復甦,競爭壓力正在加劇。在丹麥,特斯拉4月份的銷量少於中國電動車初創企業小鵬汽車,而在荷蘭則被比亞迪超越。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%87-%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-134716820.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 22:20:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "多倫多證交所開盤走低 能源板塊波動持續",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/443mFuR.RWyxq4v0qKCvcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPECAG0T8_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 加拿大主要股指週五早盤小幅下跌,能源價格降溫和地緣政治緊張情緒抑制了前一交易日大幅反彈的勢頭。截至美國東部時間09:40,S&amp;P/TSX綜合指數下跌61.12點,跌幅0.18%,報33,903.21點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一小幅回調是在週四強勁表現之後出現的,當時基準指數飆升1.94%,收於33,964.33點。藍籌股S&amp;P/TSX 60指數週五也略有回落,下跌0.21%至1,978.52點,此前在週四交易中上漲2.00%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>華爾街受科技股強勢推動創新高</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市週五開盤創下歷史新高,延續了科技板塊強勁企業財報推動的漲勢。S&amp;P 500指數攀升0.4%,創下7,237.19點的新高峰,而納斯達克綜合指數突破25,000點大關,上漲0.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-82b67c25-5a61-3e14-8146-d17b0dbdd5dd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果公司(NASDAQ:AAPL)股價在早盤交易中跳漲逾4%,此前該公司提供了樂觀的營收指引和強勁的毛利率展望。Reddit Inc(NYSE:RDDT)也獲得顯著提振,飆升近10%,因其日活躍用戶增長超出華爾街預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>油價在伊朗緊張局勢中下滑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原油價格繼續從四年高位回落,市場正在消化華盛頓與德黑蘭之間的升級威脅。布蘭特原油期貨下跌1.25%至109.02美元/桶,而WTI原油期貨下跌2.83%至102.10美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管價格下滑,但供應擔憂仍然高企,因為霍爾木茲海峽實際上已對全球運輸關閉。伊朗警告稱,如果總統唐納德·特朗普推進擬議的軍事選項,將對美國陣地發動「長期而痛苦的打擊」。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>黃金走弱 加息擔憂籠罩市場</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金價格週五下滑,徘徊在一個月低點附近,投資者正在權衡持續通脹對央行政策的影響。XAU/USD價格下跌0.27%至4,617.24美元/盎司,延續了4月份金價下跌約1%的疲軟期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯準會和其他主要央行的鷹派信號最近對無收益資產造成壓力。政策制定者越來越多地對能源驅動的通脹發出警告,暗示利率可能需要在更長時間內保持較高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%AB%E5%A4%9A%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%96%8B%E7%9B%A4%E8%B5%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-145809531.html",
